percent on average since <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1946</TIMEX> and positive since <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the 19 th century</TIMEX>.
(In our calculations, we assume <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">2.1 percent</NUMEX> real growth in dividends.)

