increase their earnings by <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">10 percent</NUMEX>, with inflation at <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">about 2 percent</NUMEX>. When
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">firms</ENAMEX> retain lots of earnings it gets more complicated, with the growth of
